{"tid":1039680,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"【英文本色】「十幾」和「廿幾」怎說？","createTime":"2019-02-27T14:39:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-02T17:49:11.000Z","uid":132461,"like":0,"dislike":36,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"b86c3bd4a9f5a5deacf7da45f3c5d0b7b27e4cc8","tid":1039680,"uid":132461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T14:39:41.000Z","msg":"很怕看見「十幾」、「廿幾」、「百幾」這些字，因為有時候真的不知道如何把這些意思傳神地翻譯成英文。<br />\n<br />\n十本書是tenbooks，十一本書是，elevenbooks，二十本是twentybooks，那麼如果你不肯定是幾多本書，想大約說是「十幾本」，英文可以怎樣處理？<br />\n<br />\n無三不成幾，十幾本書，斷估都起碼有十三本，既然如此，說therearebetween13and20books最穩陣。但當然，這樣聽起來是十分奇怪，所以方便的做法是說thereareovertenbooks或therearemorethantenbooks。<br />\n<br />\n明白的，很多語言專家都反對這個說法，因為十三係morethanten，一百萬都是morethanten。但以日常的對話來說，外國人都會理解這是「十幾」的意思。<br />\n<br />\n至於「廿幾」，我們可以說twenty-odd或twenty-plus，百幾則是onehundredodd或onehundredplus。說到這裏，也要提提表達約數的重要地方。<br />\n<br />\n大概五十人，可以說aboutfiftypeople或aroundfiftypeople。About是英國人較常用，around則較常見於北美。五十至六十人，可以有以下選擇：一，therearebetweenfiftyandsixtypeople；二，therearefiftytosixtypeople。<br />\n<br />\n記住兩點，用between就要說betweenfiftyandsixty，不能說betweenfiftytosixty。有些人會說thereareaboutfiftytosixtypeople，其實有輕微語病，因為fiftytosixty已經是一個約數，再加一個about在前面便有點多餘了。<br />\n<br />\n魏徵<br />\n酷愛英文，劉家傑是永遠偶像，幾乎背得出當年《英語一分鐘》的每集內容。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20151011/54300025\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20151011%2F54300025&d=7eOXcRQmrlFTo7mkgo38hAy7VxIBYRqzliHj24KwcnI%3D&h=63396404\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20151011%2F54300025&h=41c67f12\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20151011/54300025</a>"},{"pid":"06fffb7f0f2c2beadf01d0787ef04b8fadeb62f7","tid":1039680,"uid":224561,"like":81,"dislike":0,"score":81,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T14:49:07.000Z","msg":"屌你老母space都唔識用咪撚出文啦"},{"pid":"7d52da9156476884a2de85f6d7c41fa69df1216b","tid":1039680,"uid":66254,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T14:56:36.000Z","msg":"10ish"},{"pid":"b2eda68ee5c09c2e509ae0717e0cc65ae0017152","tid":1039680,"uid":78046,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T14:59:15.000Z","msg":"睇到咁長仲以為係德文"},{"pid":"5c16cf6b267f0df1c26f4673fec940b5ee588b2e","tid":1039680,"uid":157509,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T14:59:59.000Z","msg":"ish"},{"pid":"02784c37039a284dda4c37c648ef6b00992a1e58","tid":1039680,"uid":215270,"like":33,"dislike":0,"score":33,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T15:00:09.000Z","msg":"Twenty something"},{"pid":"348d65c5c1c1a66aee9a85020c737bb16488dab7","tid":1039680,"uid":25260,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T15:00:26.000Z","msg":"Dozens"},{"pid":"726d873f23884c47aafaa71b9d55fa81f57a6b0e","tid":1039680,"uid":186832,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T15:01:55.000Z","msg":"十幾唔知<br />\n廿幾 五十幾嗰啲就twenty something, fifty something"},{"pid":"c20f95fffe31e893a5957117034accb1368dde6c","tid":1039680,"uid":25699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T15:18:33.000Z","msg":"Ten sth"},{"pid":"29f47c1ff13e545f95952ce0b4effc1e21ed9ec1","tid":1039680,"uid":132461,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"726d873f23884c47aafaa71b9d55fa81f57a6b0e","tid":1039680,"uid":186832,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T15:01:55.000Z","msg":"十幾唔知<br />\n廿幾 五十幾嗰啲就twenty something, fifty something"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T15:21:52.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.italki.com/question/457199\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.italki.com%2Fquestion%2F457199&d=7eOXcRQmrlFTo7mkgo38hAy7VxIBYRqzliHj24KwcnI%3D&h=07195d1b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.italki.com/question/457199</a>"},{"pid":"c63f1b98e1ee02769cef4da964fe8afa6daa4e54",